      "cooked": "<p>\u2026would be really useful for SIT (sprint interval training).</p>\n<p>I don\u2019t think this is available on any other platform- would be a standout feature of trainerday <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>",
