      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2021-04-09T16:32:56.465Z",
      "cooked": "<p>So I tried manually switching between ERG and \u201cfree ride\u201d AKA resistance mode, and noticed something strange:<br>\nUsing the \u00b1 buttons had no effect for a broad range (if I remember correctly from 15 to 29%)  and than jumped way up going from 29 to 30%.  It was a jump from around 130W to 200+W in the same gear.  This was using a Kickr5 and iPad.  Is that normal?</p>",
