      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-04-10T05:27:06.420Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t exactly understand what you mean but you can go into settings and change the % of gain when you press plus minus. Kickr has both a delay as well as problems dealing with many quick power changes but it still should be reasonable to use. It should not do huge jumps but if you are in big gear you might need to change your settings.</p>",
